        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Recreation and Public Purposes Tribal Parity Act</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of the Interior to sell or lease public lands to federally recognized Indian tribes for recreational or public purposes, subject to annual acreage limitations.</p>]]>
